OL,3,CSuspected arson attack at former
OL,4,Csynagogue in east London
OL,6,FCounter-terrorism police are
OL,7,Finvestigating a suspected arson attack
OL,8,Fat a former synagogue.
OL,10,FJewish security charity Shomrim said
OL,11,Fthat fire crews were called out to the
OL,12,Fbuilding in Nelson Street,
OL,13,FWhitechapel, east London, in the early
OL,14,Fhours of Tuesday.
OL,16,FThe incident is being investigated
OL,17,Falongside a number of apparent attacks
OL,18,Fon Jewish sites in London since late
OL,19,FMarch.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/4
