PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1778155869
OL,3,CSuspected arson attack at former
OL,4,Csynagogue in east London
OL,6,FThe Metropolitan Police said officers
OL,7,Fwere called just before 5.15am by the
OL,8,FLondon Fire Brigade, and that minor
OL,9,Fdamage had been caused to a set of
OL,10,Fgates and a lock at the front of the
OL,11,Fbuilding.
OL,13,FCCTV showed that the fire had ben
OL,14,Fstarted deliberately minutes before,
OL,15,Fthe force said.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/4
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
