CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1778155869
OL,3,CSuspected arson attack at former
OL,4,Csynagogue in east London
OL,6,FDetective Chief Superintendent
OL,7,FBrittany Clarke said: "We are taking
OL,8,Fthis incident extremely seriously and
OL,9,Fwe will be working closely with
OL,10,Fcolleagues from Counter Terrorism
OL,11,FPolicing to support the investigation.
OL,13,F"The building targeted has not been
OL,14,Foperational as a synagogue for some
OL,15,Fyears but that will be of little
OL,16,Fcomfort to the Jewish community in
OL,17,FTower Hamlets, Hackney and beyond, who
OL,18,Fare first in my thoughts this morning.
OL,26,@oD@WOUuD@AOU
