OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1778155869
OL,3,CSuspected arson attack at former
OL,4,Csynagogue in east London
OL,6,F"Local residents can expect to see an
OL,7,Fincreased police presence in the area
OL,8,Fwhile inquiries into this incident
OL,9,Fcontinue."
